{"title":"debian10中文乱码的问题","date":"2023-07-28T17:40:19.049Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2023年7月28日","L":"2023/07/28","MM-DD":"07-28"},"link":"2023/07/28/debian10中文乱码的问题","updated":"2023-07-28T09:20:58.968Z","content":"<p><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/54b2c3e1de874adab33d62557bb0cd35.png\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n首先输入<code>locale</code>，查看本机语言包，发现没有中文的</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/221efa5bd7a648a9b125d7839069fd79.png\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n输入</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">dpkg-reconfigure locales</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/a45a56f2e5a74b60a64ac76afaa812f2.png\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<p>在末尾选择按空格键选中图中四个，按enter确认，最后终端选中中文utf-8的即可。<br>\n然后<code>reboot</code>重启机器<br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/97f9dc585b82475383c19d31d2f14aa6.png\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n再次<code>locale</code>查看语言环境，已经ok<br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/e33654bb409f408e89fff90fa3506e13.png\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n此时发现中文显示正常</p>\n","prev":{"title":"centos下离线安装sqlserver 无网络安装sqlserver","link":"2023/07/28/centos下离线安装sqlserver 无网络安装sqlserver"},"next":{"title":"docker push时出现denied_ requested access to the resource is denied","link":"2023/07/28/docker push时出现denied_ requested access to the resource is denied"},"plink":"http://glj520.tk/2023/07/28/debian10中文乱码的问题/","reading_time":"166 字约 1 分钟"}